{"tid":2035663,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【震驚70億人】英國人與中國人的分別","createTime":"2020-05-26T05:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T05:19:24.000Z","uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"897ee7db811ff0762bb2ebe1a3830dcfe8b775f9","tid":2035663,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:19:24.000Z","msg":"英國人來了，他們用一百多年的時間，將一個破爛不堪的小漁村打造成為東方的一顆明珠：世界上最繁華的金融和貿易中心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K38v7A2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK38v7A2.jpg&h=6110fb6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國人來了，資本家紛紛奪路而逃，這顆曾經璀璨無比的東方之珠，正以超乎想像的速度向當初那個破爛不堪的小漁村回歸。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fa3Dw2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFa3Dw2M.jpg&h=9c4c2454&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}